    "poetic_translation_prompt = \"Translate the following text from Japanese to English. The original text is a chant sung by god telling his story. Try to make the translation also look like a chant but keep the original meanings.\"\n",
    "\n",
    "descriptive_translation_prompt = \"Translate the following text from Japanese to English. The original text is a chant sung by god telling his story. Use a story telling tone. Keep the original meanings.\""
