      "Two young men, I saw them stride,\n",
      "Toward my mire, side by side.\n",
      "\n",
      "The first, a hero, strong and bright,\n",
      "A godlike beauty, filled with light.\n",
      "The second, sickly, pale of face,\n",
      "A wretched air, a foul disgrace.\n",
      "\n",
