      "\n",
      "Again, the young man said, \"Is that your Yukar? Your Sakehau? I would like to hear it closer.\"\n",
      "\n",
      "My heart swelled with joy! I hopped to the corner of the upper hearth and sang, \"Toh-ro-ro Han-ro-ku Han-ro-ku!\"\n",
      "\n",
