      "\n",
      "Kappa Reu Reu Kappa,\n",
      "One day, along the stream I played,\n",
      "Swimming down to Samayunkur's place,\n",
      "Where maidens drew water, fair of face.\n",
      "\n",
      "Samayunkur's sister, a vision bright,\n",
      "Bucket in hand, cattails held tight,\n",
